            <div class="chapter__primary">
                <h1 class="chapter__heading--merriweather-font">In 2018, <br>the federal government<span class="chapter__big-number">
                    collected $3.3
                    <span class="chapter__big-number--anecdote-placement">
                        trillion.
                        <section class="anecdote">
                            <h1 class="anecdote__heading">Did you know?</h1>
                            <span class="anecdote__button--text hidden">How can I visualize our Federal Revenue?</span>
                            <div class="anecdote__panes">
